{"tid":588861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每個人都曾經有嘅奇怪幻想","createTime":"2018-03-11T13:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T14:25:24.000Z","uid":173458,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7be2b5a5266466a7b38ebf292c73a8d22d38091e","tid":588861,"uid":173458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺現實生活中，成日都會喺自己個腦到做一啲賭博。例如可能跑步嘅時候，就會諗如果慢過隔離嗰個就會失去重要嘅野。見到垃圾，又會諗如果執咗佢就會有錢，唔執又會有啲後果。<br />\n<br />\n講到1999，有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb4bd1e5f414439441ba1c12ea6f8cbfbbe0c73","tid":588861,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"瞓覺個時有時瞓唔著會幻想床邊有隻鬼 我要用被由頭笠到腳指尾郁都唔郁得 如果一郁就比佢發現咗 到時唔知發生咩事 之後慢慢咁瞓著咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bbded576a094d15d9194e7e7fcc0289802fdc9","tid":588861,"uid":9104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.dopl3r.com/memes_files/wonder-if-hes-thinking-about-me-ineed-to-reach-that-tree-before-that-car-or-ill-die-aXm8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.dopl3r.com%2Fmemes_files%2Fwonder-if-hes-thinking-about-me-ineed-to-reach-that-tree-before-that-car-or-ill-die-aXm8X.jpg&h=59bb82ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec3116bfde40205c6ba1e0af4448844055844268","tid":588861,"uid":28402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:07:22.000Z","msg":"過馬路時心諗如果時光倒退一分鐘前（即係紅燈既時段），我一定比車車死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b18f104b9473bbe1c289bb52eec1d2778388804","tid":588861,"uid":59887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:08:57.000Z","msg":"上堂會諗住有人渣AK47入黎  然後自己要第一時間呢係枱底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9089287e5c7bc85e99fbc158093d9b5d58e595ef","tid":588861,"uid":164457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:10:14.000Z","msg":"商場唔可以踩唔同顏色嘅地板 踩中就中地雷死"},{"pid":"82591cb5158a882adee120cbec12878e75919970","tid":588861,"uid":164457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:12:15.000Z","msg":"以前幻想就嚟翻到學校嘅時候中槍 要點樣捱翻去再暈底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4632462fc94e7f7921921aa2a696c87562659e8","tid":588861,"uid":97497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:22:05.000Z","msg":"宇宙其實只係人體裡面一部份 即係一個人裏𥚃面又有一個宇宙 唔同嘅星球、隕石  只係啲細胞、腫瘤 我哋一直保育 令地球環境美好 其實唔想細胞病變 <br />\n大個先發現之前諗嘢係幾咁冇科學根據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係都好懷念以前無限制嘅想像空間 依家有知識後大腦已經直接講無可能 唔洗諗"},{"pid":"e749bcff4170845abc33dddb8ce2ac7205221e23","tid":588861,"uid":118179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b18f104b9473bbe1c289bb52eec1d2778388804","tid":588861,"uid":59887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:08:57.000Z","msg":"上堂會諗住有人渣AK47入黎  然後自己要第一時間呢係枱底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"諗過如果有個傻佬揸住槍衝入課室，邊個位嘅人會死先，同邊個位最安全"}]}